<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Japanese_language&amp;action=edit&amp;section=20" title="Edit section: Notes">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Notes">Notes</span></h2>
<div class="reflist references-column-count references-column-count-2" style="column-count: 2; -moz-column-count: 2; -webkit-column-count: 2; list-style-type: decimal;">
<ol class="references">
